  <td>$129/mo (Connect, 5 users)</td>
  <td>~$250/mo per tech</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>Growth tier</td>
  <td>$249/mo (Grow, 15 users)</td>
  <td>~$300/mo per tech</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>5-tech team cost</td>
  <td>$129-249/mo total</td>
  <td>$1,000-1,500/mo total</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>10-tech team cost</td>
  <td>$249/mo total</td>
  <td>$2,000-3,000/mo total</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>Free trial</td>
  <td>14 days, no credit card</td>
  <td>No — demo required</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>Contract</td>
  <td>Month-to-month</td>
  <td>Annual contract typical</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
              <div class="verdict-strip mt-4">
                <p class="text-sm">
                  <strong>Price Reality Check:</strong> For a 10-technician HVAC company, Jobber costs roughly <strong>$249/month</strong> while ServiceTitan costs roughly <strong>$2,000-3,000/month</strong>. That is an 8-12x price difference. ServiceTitan needs to generate significantly more revenue or savings to justify that cost.
                </p>
