  <td>$25,140-37,140</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
              <p class="text-sm text-foreground/70 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
                The Jobber stack costs roughly <strong>$5,000/year</strong> while the ServiceTitan stack costs <strong>$25,000-37,000/year</strong>. The question is whether ServiceTitan's advanced reporting, marketing attribution, and sales tools generate at least $20,000-32,000 in additional annual revenue or savings. For companies doing $3M+ in revenue, the answer is often yes. For companies under $1.5M, it rarely is.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div id="migration" class="mt-10">
              <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-2xl mb-4">Migration Difficulty</h2>
              <table class="comparison-table">
<thead><tr>
  <th>Factor</th>
  <th>Jobber → ServiceTitan</th>
  <th>ServiceTitan → Jobber</th>
</tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
