              <p class="text-sm text-foreground/70 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
                The most common migration path is <strong>Jobber → ServiceTitan</strong> as companies grow past 15 technicians and need deeper reporting. The reverse migration (ServiceTitan → Jobber) happens when companies decide the cost difference is not justified by the features they actually use.
              </p>
