                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-0.5">→</span> You have fewer than 15 technicians</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-0.5">→</span> Your annual revenue is under $3M</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-0.5">→</span> You want to be up and running in days, not months</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-0.5">→</span> Budget is a primary concern</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-0.5">→</span> You value simplicity over feature depth</li>
