                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">→</span> You sell maintenance memberships and equipment</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">→</span> You have dedicated office/operations staff</li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">→</span> Data-driven growth is your strategy</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

